title: Desert Island Discs - The Comedians Edition  (BBC)
description:
Devised by Roy Plomley
Presented by Kirsty Young, Roy Plomley, Michael Parkinson, Sue Lawley
Format: MP3
Bitrate: 160 Kbps

54 Episodes
Over 37 Hours
147kbps - 183kbps

Desert Island Discs was created by Roy Plomley in 1942, and the format is simple: a guest is invited by Kirsty Young to choose the eight records they would take with them to a desert island.

A collection of comedian related episodes of the BBC's Desert Island Discs. Episodes from 1975 to May 2014.



Enjoy and Seed!!
